
FlindersRedbox-createRdrWebPage
===============================

createRdrWebPage-demo-v1.0
--------------------------
Initial version. Allows a web administrator to quickly create a
static web page from the command line. The web page can include
page title, page description and a description of every file
within the web directory (with a corresponding hyperlink).

createRdrWebPage-demo-v1.0.1
----------------------------
- Replaced IGNORE_FILE_LIST with the regex list, IGNORE_FILE_REGEX_LIST.
  (This improvement in flexibility made it easier to use with STEN. See
  https://github.com/grantj-re3/SimpleTemplateENgine-Sten.)
- Updated to detect broken symlinks.
- Updated doco.

